net.floodlightcontroller.util

Class FlowModUtils

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.floodlightcontroller.util.FlowModUtils

  • public class FlowModUtils
extends java.lang.Object
    Convert an OFFlowMod to a specific OFFlowMod-OFFlowModCommand. These function as setCommand(OFFlowModCommand) methods for an OFFlowMod. Used initially in the static flow pusher, but will likely find merit elsewhere. Other useful FlowMod utility functions and constants are also included.
    Author:
    Ryan Izard
